useradd deepak
passwd deepak 
grep deepak /etc/passwd 
id deepak 
groups deepak 


how to modify comment field of any user ?
usermod -c "Itadmin" deepak 
grep deepak /etc/deepak 

how to change login shell of any user ?
usermod -s /sbin/nologin 
grep natasha /etc/passwd 

how to add user with specific userID and groupID ?
useradd -u 3000 harry 
passwd  harry 
grep harry /etc/passwd 
grep harry /etc/group 
id harry 
usermod -u 4000 harry 
grep harry /etc/passwd 
grep harry /etc/group 
groupmod -g 5000 harry 
grep harry /etc/passwd 
grep harry /etc/group 


how to change login name or account name of an user?
usermod -l neeraj sarah 
su -sarah 
su -neeraj 

how to lock and unlock any user account ?
useradd rajeev 
passwd rajeev 
usermod -L rajeev 
passwd -l rajeev 
passwd -S rajeev 
passwd -u rajeev 
usermod -U rajeev 
passwd -s rajeev 
 
how to delete password prompt for any user ?
useradd deep 
passwd -d deep 
su -deepak 
su -deep
now you can set password of this user if it is required passwd deep 

useradd monika /etc/passwd 
grep monika /etc/passwd 
grep monika /etc/shadow 
passwd monika 

grep monika /etc/shadow 
passwd -l monika 

grep monika /etc/shadow 
passwd -u monika 

grep monika /etc/shadow 
passwd -d monika 

grep monika /etc/shadow 
passwd monika 







